# Project-1 integration harness

This repo is the **reference harness** for OKF + Forge + dispatch integration — not a minimal product scaffold.

## Do

- Keep full integration spec: `docs/okf-forge-integration-spec.md`.
- Record test evidence under `.okf/tests/*-evidence.md` for vertical slices and E2E smokes.
- Maintain complete promotion checklists under `.okf/workflows/forge-*-checklist.md`.
- Run `scripts/okf-validate`, `scripts/okf-check-adapters`, `scripts/okf-check-forge-receipts` before claiming integration complete.
- Promote **stable, generic** patterns to bootstrap templates after harness proof.

## Do not

- Assume generated bootstrap products include full harness checklists or adversarial dossiers.
- Remove harness-only evidence to “simplify” without updating the integration spec.
- Use legacy ai-task MCP (`scripts/mcp/`) for new harness work — use OKF dispatch and Forge MCPs.

## Cursor rules

Product-oriented rules (`okf-ecosystem-routing`, forge operator, dispatch, promotion) apply here too. This rule adds harness-specific expectations on top.
